  "texts": [
    "The R_ref then sends the required optimizations, which we call the optimization scheme, to the R_adv.",
    "The R_adv queries the LLM for rectification measures, i.e., how to edit the decompiler output to achieve the optimization scheme from the R_ref.",
    "As discussed before, various optimizations can help each other.",
    "Thus, the R_adv will sort the received various optimizations in the scheme and prioritize the optimizations that can provide additional guidance for subsequent optimizations.",
    "The output of the R_adv is the latest version of the decompiler output, which adopts the rectification measures from LLM."
  ],
